*The folder contains all the files for the Joomla Site Installation.

1. Upload all the files in this folder to the webhsting folder. Eg: http://www.kvm.com/
2. Open the uploaded url in web browser. eg: www.kvm.com/
3. The web browser displays all the files in the directory. If not open the file "kickstart.php" from the uploaded folder.
Eg: www.kvm.com/kickstart.php
4. An installation window will open and it guides you to provide the mysql database information and website information.
5. Once done, the website will be live on the uploaded url. Eg: www.kvm.com

*****************************